{"tid":882042,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癡線 大陸飲食節目係咁叫人食檳榔","createTime":"2018-10-30T01:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:16:47.000Z","uid":80481,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"64d38d9ec5cc0daccff6956f9c8d289820e2864f","tid":882042,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/095658_a9217932d1dbb0d54bf5e71bc27f7c40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F095658_a9217932d1dbb0d54bf5e71bc27f7c40.png&h=d88379e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/095653_8bbbe430bfc3d4a9e427f08fffa6db73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F095653_8bbbe430bfc3d4a9e427f08fffa6db73.png&h=63adc643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/095704_73c5ff8cd0734a780f70db9ba6944049.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F095704_73c5ff8cd0734a780f70db9ba6944049.png&h=88ae3f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/095708_26bf8c831d9e1bc7bc2a124a88141931.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F095708_26bf8c831d9e1bc7bc2a124a88141931.png&h=8b16b11d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n檳榔包含檳榔鹼、檳榔素、檳榔定、多酚化合物等成份，可以讓人有興奮、保暖的效果，所以有人就藉著嚼檳榔提神。但是2003年國際癌症研究中心（IARC）已確認檳榔內的多項檳榔生物鹼都是一級致癌物，會引起口腔黏膜病變，造成黏膜纖維化，導致口腔黏膜變硬，嘴巴會漸漸打不開，接觸食物時，敏感疼痛。"},{"pid":"4afea70f7a273f25b3a7dfef731dafff327b1fef","tid":882042,"uid":6532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"李蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cb7aa408ed5a2f804cf25e9434f76035136858","tid":882042,"uid":34223,"like":16